data.description: Just Listed!! Beautiful, move-in ready 2 bedroom, 3 bathroom, 2 car garage home located in Sunset Hills Country Club Subdivision. 1,653 Sq Ft. home sits on a spacious double lot of 0.34 of an acre on a quite street with no HOA fees. Includes a seasonal room with a hot tub, outbuilding with electric, patio with a grilling fire-pit and a second drive way to park RV or boat. Only 0.9 miles to Fred Howard Park and beach. Minutes from restaurants and Historic downtown Tarpon Springs. Make an offer on this remarkable property!
